---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="KlawAgent Terms of Service — the rules of the road.">

<style>
.doc-hero { background:var(--text); color:#fff; padding:80px 48px; text-align:center; }
.doc-hero .eyebrow { font-size:0.68rem; letter-spacing:.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--accent); font-weight:700; margin-bottom:16px; }
.doc-hero h1 { font-family:var(--serif); font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem); font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin-bottom:12px; }
.doc-hero .date { font-size:0.875rem; color:#a09080; }
.doc-body { max-width:760px; margin:0 auto; padding:64px 48px 96px; }
.summary-card { background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--border-light); border-left:4px solid var(--accent); border-radius:16px; padding:28px 32px; margin-bottom:56px; }
.summary-card .lbl { font-size:0.68rem; letter-spacing:.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--accent); font-weight:700; margin-bottom:10px; }
.summary-card p { font-size:1.05rem; font-style:italic; color:var(--muted); }
.doc-section { margin-bottom:48px; }
.doc-section h2 { font-family:var(--serif); font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:20px; padding-bottom:12px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-light); color:var(--text); }
.doc-section p { font-size:0.9375rem; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.75; margin-bottom:12px; }
.check-list { list-style:none; padding:0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; }
.check-list li { display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:10px; font-size:0.9375rem; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.6; }
.check-list li::before { content:"✓"; color:var(--accent); font-weight:700; flex-shrink:0; margin-top:2px; }
.x-list { list-style:none; padding:0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; }
.x-list li { display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:10px; font-size:0.9375rem; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.6; }
.x-list li::before { content:"✕"; color:var(--accent); font-weight:700; flex-shrink:0; margin-top:2px; }
.contact-card { background:var(--text); color:#fff; border-radius:20px; padding:40px 32px; text-align:center; margin-top:56px; }
.contact-card h2 { font-family:var(--serif); font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin-bottom:10px; }
.contact-card p { color:#a09080; margin-bottom:24px; font-size:0.9375rem; }
.contact-card a { display:inline-block; background:var(--accent); color:#fff; border-radius:999px; padding:12px 28px; font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.1em; text-transform:uppercase; transition:background .2s; }
.contact-card a:hover { background:#991b1b; }
@media(max-width:640px) { .doc-hero { padding:60px 24px; } .doc-body { padding:48px 24px 72px; } }
</style>

<div class="doc-hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
  <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
  <p class="date">Last updated: February 19, 2026</p>
</div>

<div class="doc-body">

  <div class="summary-card">
    <div class="lbl">The Short Version</div>
    <p>Use KlawAgent for legitimate business purposes. Don't abuse the service. Pay on time. We'll do our job and you do yours.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-section">
    <h2>The Service</h2>
    <p>KlawAgent provides a managed AI agent platform ("the Service") built on the OpenClaw framework. We deploy, host, and maintain AI agents on your behalf on a dedicated server. By using the Service, you agree to these terms.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-section">
    <h2>Your Responsibilities</h2>
    <ul class="check-list">
      <li>Provide accurate information when signing up</li>
      <li>Keep your account credentials secure</li>
      <li>Only connect integrations you are authorized to use</li>
      <li>Use the Service in compliance with applicable laws</li>
      <li>Pay your monthly platform fee on time</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-section">
    <h2>Acceptable Use</h2>
    <p>You may not use KlawAgent to:</p>
    <ul class="x-list">
      <li>Send spam or unsolicited bulk communications</li>
      <li>Violate any applicable law or regulation</li>
      <li>Harass, threaten, or harm any individual</li>
      <li>Scrape or harvest data without authorization</li>
      <li>Attempt to reverse-engineer or compromise the platform</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-section">
    <h2>Billing</h2>
    <p>The platform fee is billed monthly. AI API usage costs (OpenAI, Anthropic, etc.) are billed separately at cost plus a transparent margin, detailed in your monthly usage report. Failure to pay may result in suspension of the Service. We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee on your first month.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-section">
    <h2>Cancellation</h2>
    <p>You may cancel at any time with 30 days notice. Upon cancellation, your server and data will be decommissioned. We recommend exporting any data you need before cancelling.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-section">
    <h2>Data &amp; Privacy</h2>
    <p>Your data is stored on your dedicated server. KlawAgent accesses it only to operate your agent. We do not sell your data. See our <a href="/privacy" style="color:var(--accent);text-decoration:underline">Privacy Policy</a> for full details.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-section">
    <h2>Liability</h2>
    <p>KlawAgent provides the Service "as is." We are not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the Service, including actions taken by your AI agent. You are responsible for reviewing agent outputs before acting on them.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-section">
    <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
    <p>We may update these terms from time to time. We'll give you at least 14 days notice of significant changes via email. Continued use of the Service after changes take effect constitutes acceptance.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-section">
    <h2>Governing Law</h2>
    <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Texas, United States. Any disputes will be resolved in Travis County, Texas.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="contact-card">
    <h2>Questions About These Terms?</h2>
    <p>We're real people in Austin, Texas. Just ask.</p>
    <a href="mailto:hey@klawagent.ai">hey@klawagent.ai</a>
  </div>

</div>

</Layout>
